item.title: CVE-2018-7990|2024-08-05T06:37:59.688Z -- huawei%20technologies%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- mate10%20pro
item.description: Mate10 Pro Huawei smart phones with the versions before 8.1.0.326(C00) have a FRP bypass vulnerability. During the mobile phone reseting process, an attacker could bypass "Find My Phone" protect after a series of voice and keyboard operations. Successful exploit could allow an attacker to bypass FRP.
